    I had tight valves on an engine with brand new VW heads, ended up that
the heads had bad seats from the factory.  Had to have a valve job, new
seats and new exhaust guides after less than 10K miles.  Been fine since
then.

    Anybody else getting bad seats from new Brazilian heads? (1600 DP)

